===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Steven (Masters)}}
Steven forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Steven|Metagross}}, {{rf|Alolan}} {{p|Sandslash}}, {{Shiny}} {{p|Rayquaza}}, {{p|Deoxys}}, {{p|Cradily}}, Shiny {{p|Stoutland}}, and {{p|Skarmory}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Both his Metagross and Shiny Rayquaza are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]], while his Deoxys can change into any of its {{form|Deoxys|Formes}}. Steven has been featured on the title screen since the game's release and became a playable sync pair on February 14, 2020.

Steven has also made notable appearances in two of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]] and the [[Arceus arc]].

